42void
43der_free_general_string (heim_general_string *str)
44{
45 free(*str);
46 *str = NULL;
47}
48
49void
50der_free_integer (int *i)
51{
52 *i = 0;
53}
54
55void
56der_free_integer64 (int64_t *i)
57{
58 *i = 0;
59}
60
61void
62der_free_unsigned (unsigned *u)
63{
64 *u = 0;
65}
66
67void
68der_free_unsigned64 (uint64_t *u)
69{
70 *u = 0;
71}
72
73void
74der_free_generalized_time(time_t *t)
75{
76 *t = 0;
77}
78
79void
80der_free_utctime(time_t *t)
81{
82 *t = 0;
83}

85
86void
87der_free_utf8string (heim_utf8_string *str)
88{
89 free(*str);
90 *str = NULL;
91}
92
93void
94der_free_printable_string (heim_printable_string *str)
95{
96 der_free_octet_string(str);
97}
98
99void
100der_free_ia5_string (heim_ia5_string *str)
101{
102 der_free_octet_string(str);
103}
104
105void
106der_free_bmp_string (heim_bmp_string *k)
107{
108 free(k->data);
109 k->data = NULL;
110 k->length = 0;
111}
112

114der_free_universal_string (heim_universal_string *k)

118 k->length = 0;
119}

129der_free_octet_string (heim_octet_string *k)

134}

137der_free_heim_integer (heim_integer *k)

144void
145der_free_oid (heim_oid *k)
146{

150}
